    "testimonials_mB6iUg": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "image_KJynVq": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>Victiles is lucky to have someone like Mehak on the team! She is the best! Big thank you to Mehak for her outstanding service. She was incredibly helpful, polite, and made us feel very welcomed.<br/>Her knowledge and dedication made the entire experience smooth and enjoyable. You can tell she genuinely cares about customers. She is the BEST.<br/>Highly recommend victiles, had a wonderful experience of amazing service because of her!</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "Joe",
            "date": "June 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pOUlNrMVBVVUZwWTNGa01ITlNUR2czT0VORlkwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjNRSk1PUUFpY3FkMHNSTGg3OENFY0E%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=451efdae-fca6-4c4a-811a-6e1728b8c953"
          }
        },
        "image_dNXyHf": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>The Best Tiles Place with the Finest Service - Mehak & Damien helped us from the beginning till the end - Extremely Professional and Highly Skilled Staff - Both Mehak & Damien treated our little 2 Bathroom Project as their own and helped making it a Success - Vic Tiles has a great collection of tiles to suit every budget - And Top Service with a Smile - Highly Recommended.</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed_8acaa720-f68c-4b63-9d63-5d329e8a2c4c.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "Satish Nair",
            "date": "March 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xweVNYSTFWMWhRUW10cU5FRTRVVnB6TmpsMWRHYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlpySXI1V1hQQmtqNEE4UVpzNjl1dGc%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=b4920244-5f64-4dbd-b237-76832e7fe342"
          }
        },
        "image_ArCqVm": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>Bill and Mehak was so helpful, friendly and provided exceptional service in picking tiles. He gave great advice with plenty of options. Didn’t pressure to buy and gave a great price. Come and see Bill if you need tiles</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed_8a7248cc-6308-4d15-86b4-c1b8248a9fb3.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "Benny Maison",
            "date": "June 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xvNVpXUXRWemhmVDI1NVJUZE9WMHhDV0U1VmNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlo5ZWQtVzhfT255RTdOV0xCWE5VclE%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=1a8fa274-7a1a-4514-9e4a-11f994482d05"
          }
        },
        "image_6xRWWd": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>Mehak and Bill were absolutely phenomenal from start to finish.<br/><br/>Right from the get-go, they were incredibly patient, attentive, and helped point me in the right direction when choosing tiles. The level of service was truly outstanding. Everything they said would happen happened exactly as promised, and they looked after me extremely well.<br/><br/>Victiles has a phenomenal selection of tiles and a beautiful range on display, with so many options. The showroom made the decision-making process much easier, and the team were always available to offer helpful advice without being pushy.<br/><br/>Nothing was ever too much trouble, and the communication throughout the entire process was top-notch. When we realised we hadn't ordered enough tiles and needed more in a hurry, Mehak immediately jumped into action, kept me updated every step of the way, and even arranged for the additional tiles to be delivered directly from the supplier to our home.<br/><br/>On top of all that, they're just a genuinely great bunch of people to deal with—friendly, approachable, and always willing to help. Their customer service made what could have been a stressful process incredibly easy and enjoyable.<br/><br/>I genuinely can't speak highly enough of the service, professionalism, friendliness, and customer care provided by Mehak & Bill. They really went above and beyond. Highly recommended!</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed_696b2403-42dc-4363-84be-5071f80d7a03.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "Ronnie B",
            "date": "June 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWa2RXaG9UV1pJZGtoWExXZHdiREJwYW1wUGQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjVkdWhoTWZIdkhXLWdwbDBpampPd3c%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=d32b745a-54d1-491b-9d9c-dcb4104cd5d4"
          }
        },
        "image_UkjCAq": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>Highly recommend VIC Tiles! Mehak & Damien went above and beyond to provide exceptional service and advice.<br/>Thank you!!!</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed_2fc138a7-2830-48c6-805e-c40cb4512f5b.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "Ali Kurtdereli",
            "date": "April 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKUFpHTkpPWFp2ZUZnMmJqZFNlalJNVDNsMlpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlJPZGNJOXZveFg2bjdSejRMT3l2ZGc%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=515ad77e-23a7-4e89-ba20-9248c459ac93"
          }
        },
        "image_ebm39F": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "text": "<p>I honestly couldn’t be happier with my experience at VICTiles in Dandenong!<br/><br/>I purchased my bathroom Tiles, Mosaic, Bathware, and Hybrid flooring all from VICTiles, and the whole process was so much smoother than I expected. A huge thank you to Elaine — she was incredibly patient, professional, and genuinely helpful. I visited the showroom almost every day for an entire week trying to finalise my selections (yes, I’m very indecisive!), and she supported me the whole way without ever making me feel rushed or pressured.<br/><br/>What I really loved is that I could choose everything in one place — Tiles, Mosaic feature pieces, Bathware, and Hybrid flooring — which saved me so much time running between different stores. The pricing was very competitive too, so it truly felt like I was saving money while still getting beautiful, high-quality products.<br/><br/>If you’re renovating or building, I highly recommend VICTiles. Great range, great value, and amazing service. I’m so excited to see everything come together in my new bathroom!</p>",
            "desktop_image": "shopify://shop_images/unnamed_e0f890cb-c65f-4928-b4a9-b89b5bd2b276.png",
            "large_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "mobile_screen_logo_width": 100,
            "author": "RONG ZHAN",
            "date": "March 2026",
            "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SeFZ6Qm1PSGRqY0ZoU05reEVRWE5UY1ZwVVdrRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa2ff0e8f59bfb6c3!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmRxVzBmOHdjcFhSNkxEQXNTcVpUWkE%7C%7C?entry=tts&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUzMS4wIPu8ASoASAFQAw%3D%3D&skid=bb3836e7-8c0b-4253-8d8d-8a05fb118c7f"
          }
        }
      },
