        "text_6EBK3b": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>VICTILES is a preferred choice for homeowners, builders, and renovators looking for high-quality tiles in Melbourne. We offer competitive pricing, a wide selection of products, and expert guidance to make your renovation or build seamless.</p><p>With a strong reputation for service and quality, we continue to be a trusted name for Melbourne tiles.</p>",
