          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Melbourne’s Trusted Tile Store",
            "disable_on_mobile": false,
            "size_heading": 100,
            "size_heading_mobile": 100
          }
        },
        "text_eTM7jV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At VICTILES, we supply a wide range of tiles in Melbourne for bathrooms, kitchens, living areas, and outdoor spaces. Our collection includes ceramic tiles, porcelain tiles, feature tiles, and timber-look flooring designed to suit every style and budget. </p><p>As a leading supplier of Melbourne tiles, we focus on quality, affordability, and expert advice to help you complete your project with confidence.</p>",
